{"abstract": "Among 200 top chief executives in 2012, the median compensation package jumped 16 percent. So much for the idea that shareholders are getting through to companies about reining in pay.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/30/business/an-unstoppable-climb-in-ceo-pay.html", "snippet": "Among 200 top chief executives in 2012, the median compensation package jumped 16 percent. So much for the idea that shareholders are getting through to companies about reining in pay.", "lead_paragraph": "WHEN we made our annual foray into the executive pay gold mine in April, chief executives\u2019 earnings for 2012 showed what appeared to be muted growth on the year. The $14 million in median overall compensation received by the top 100 C.E.O.\u2019s was just a 2.8 percent increase over 2011, the figures showed.", "print_section": "BU", "print_page": "1", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/06/30/business/30gret-hp/30gret-hp-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 400, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2013/06/30/business/30gret-hp/30gret-hp-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 400}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/06/30/business/30gret-hp/30gret-hp-jumbo.jpg", "height": 683, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/06/30/business/30gret-hp/30gret-hp-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 768, "width": 1152, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/06/30/business/30gret-hp/30gret-hp-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_nam